Class.name: Strix.Resultset.Request
Class.Description: Information for requesting a page from a resultset

Property.name: ResultsetId
Property.Description: The id of the resultset containing all results.

Property.name: PageSize
Property.Description: The number of items to return for one page of results

Property.name: PageNumber
Property.Description: The (one-based) number of the page to return

Property.name: SessionKey
Property.Description: The session key (normaly: login id) for this request. Only used server-side.
